Virus War
=========

A ripoff of tentacle wars
http://www.kongregate.com/games/gamezhero/tentacle-wars


Need Ruby 1.8.7, Ruby Gnome2, ruby SDL


Linux:
======

sudo apt-get install ruby (1.8.7)
test with "ruby -v"

sudo apt-get install ruby-gnome2
sudo apt-get install libsdl1.2-dev
sudo apt-get install libsdl-mixer1.2-dev
sudo gem install rubysdl


Windows
=======

Install Ruby 1.8.7
http://rubyinstaller.org/

Then RubySDL:
Read:  http://www.kmc.gr.jp/~ohai/rubysdl_download.en.html
1) Download rubysdl-win32-bin on rubyforge (http://rubyforge.org/frs/?group_id=1006)
2) go to the directory and type ruby install_rubysdl.rb


========================
Then run
ruby main.rb

